summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of Emerson Street from 15th Avenue West to West Emerson Place, and certain other streets and avenues, by grading paving the same, constructing viaducts, etc.; appropriating additional funds therefor; increasing the contribution from the Great Northern Railway Company; and amending Section 7 of Ordinance No. 77811 as amended by Ordinance No. 79326.
